Author: CircleShapedBird
Text: Safe foods really unsettle me because if I turn to my safe foods I know I'm getting desperate.... So I'll try some pizza and prove to myself I can do this.   Thank you for your comment, stay safe <3

Author: strangernumberone
Text: I'm so sorry for what you're going through. The fact that you want to keep it down is a good thing. Maybe get some safe foods that you think will have a better chance?
